      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAILPLANE (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 16.97 beating HAPPY BUDDHA. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. HAPPY BUDDHA (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish a neck away in second (16.97) behind Sailaway Gin at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to his credit. Overdue and gets his chance. THICK AS THIEVES (8) turned in a fair run last time from the squeeze finishing fifth by 3.5 lengths (16.87). Form here at this distance is sound. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ONE KNEE NONI (2) is in form and must include among the chances.",
